@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sdihot(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.28 / tmp + 0.12)) - v1)
    tmp = ((tmp * wp.sin(v0 + 0.46)) / wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp + 0.85)))
    v2 = v2
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin(0.01))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
